@startuml
skinparam ClassAttributeIconSize 0

class DatabaseConfig <<Singleton>> {
    - {static} logger : Logger
    - {static} PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME : String
    - {static} uniqueInstance : DatabaseConfig
    - entityManagerFactory : EntityManagerFactory
    - entityManagerThreadLocal : ThreadLocal<EntityManager>
    --
    - DatabaseConfig()
    + {static} getInstance() : DatabaseConfig
    + getEntityManager() : EntityManager
}

note right of DatabaseConfig
  **Eager Singleton**
  - Khởi tạo instance ngay khi class load.
  - Luôn an toàn về mặt đa luồng.
end note

@enduml
